"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"## My search for an acre of escape\\n\\n[![Paul Greenberg](https://miro.medium.com/fit/c/56/56/1\\\\*tPfbBeQ23qMKUptWlw1FaQ.jpeg)](https://4fishgreenberg.medium.com/?source=post_page-----82252fbaae82-----------------------------------)\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*lvzvn8HdxUe8BXEsPxlZ5w.png)\\n\\n“Granite erratic, Dudmaston” by Richard Webb is licensed under CC BY-SA 2.0. To view a copy of this license, visit <https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.0/?ref=openverse&atype=rich>\\n\\nIt was the rock that caught my eye. Dappled with lichen and lighted by the afternoon sun, it appeared to be the perfect place for contemplation. A spot where you could sit and write your novel, ponder your place in the universe, and perhaps reach some kind of equilibrium with the planet.\\n\",\"timestamp\":1641037730,\"title\":\"Is Anywhere Safe from Climate Change? - Paul Greenberg - Medium\"},\"digest\":\"MKoKVl2BMoPPtc0_huKX6M_In-OSyzcdI5znX0r1blQ\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x53B6D8bC323e501CF4da2bEF94509788A684654f\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"8FtxGbRbWPWQb7940KzxGqG2jivJ2oG8RE4HbumoUfQ\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"xhbjv5QpDk9xYGyMeYNYg6VSpciOkTl49nxtB5Mq3JE\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"Eq1b1WO7BNSsO6at6298iF6e0ULdgW9jnL0qbvdXG3PPTpQiJqxgs536C8116IZLxb4cQkKioxe4AdhgRdHK_Q\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x1efa2fb5e6e91bd271b4573f42746e502912f08037ac3510517bf7cf52495d00605308a6f93a88a9b002d18215ecc0cac94d0a13a95903870080eb15f187aaec1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"8FtxGbRbWPWQb7940KzxGqG2jivJ2oG8RE4HbumoUfQ\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"xhbjv5QpDk9xYGyMeYNYg6VSpciOkTl49nxtB5Mq3JE\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"origi